1:39:27.559 --> 1:39:31.188
Well, if it isn't Dale Doback
and his little butt buddy.

1:39:31.363 --> 1:39:33.388
Sticks and stones
may break my bones...

1:39:33.565 --> 1:39:37.057
...but I'm gonna kick you repeatedly
in the balls, Gardocki!

1:39:37.235 --> 1:39:39.635
Let's get them!

1:40:26.084 --> 1:40:28.814
- Where do you think you're going?
- Home.

1:40:28.987 --> 1:40:32.047
- We got something to show you.
- Come on.

1:40:32.757 --> 1:40:35.885
- You see that white dog crap?
- Do you see it?!

1:40:36.161 --> 1:40:38.425
- Yeah.
- Not too fun down there, is it?

1:40:38.597 --> 1:40:39.825
- No.
- You see?

1:40:39.998 --> 1:40:41.761
Your actions have consequences!

1:40:41.933 --> 1:40:46.802
When you oppress people,
they rise up in a fiery anger!

1:40:47.339 --> 1:40:48.567
Go home.

1:40:50.275 --> 1:40:53.574
We're not like you.
We're grown-ups, motherfucker!

1:40:53.745 --> 1:40:57.738
Say hi to your dad.
We went to high school together.

1:41:03.655 --> 1:41:06.021
The cops'll be here soon.

1:41:06.892 --> 1:41:09.417
I guess this is what it feels like
to be grown up.

1:41:09.594 --> 1:41:11.084
Hey.

1:41:11.596 --> 1:41:13.359
Can I ask you something?

1:41:13.532 --> 1:41:14.999
Yeah, of course.

1:41:15.166 --> 1:41:16.895
You know back when
you first moved in?

1:41:17.068 --> 1:41:18.092
Yeah.

1:41:18.270 --> 1:41:20.864
- Did you touch my drum set?
- No, I didn't.

1:41:21.039 --> 1:41:23.166
No, really, I won't get mad.
I just wanna know.

1:41:23.341 --> 1:41:25.241
No, I know.
You said you wouldn't get mad.

1:41:25.410 --> 1:41:28.106
I'm saying I didn't do it.
I didn't do it, I never did it.

1:41:28.280 --> 1:41:30.111
- Then I owe you an apology.
- No.

1:41:30.282 --> 1:41:31.407
No, you don't, at all.
No.

1:41:32.083 --> 1:41:34.551
Why wouldn't you take an apology
if you didn't do it?

1:41:34.719 --> 1:41:37.552
Just because I'm cool.
It doesn't matter.

1:45:18.243 --> 1:45:19.676
You got my passport.

1:45:20.812 --> 1:45:21.836
I'm good.

1:45:25.650 --> 1:45:28.619
Don't worry, not gonna be late.
Don't worry.
